AnyEvent-MtGox-Stream
=====================

This module provides an interface to the MtGox streaming API.

INSTALLATION

To install this module type the following:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install

DEPENDENCIES

This module requires these other modules and libraries:

    AnyEvent
    AnyEvent::HTTP
    JSON
    Protocol::WebSocket
    Test::More
    URI

